<plot>An unconventional foray into hauntingly enchanted territories. The carnivalesque incantation is accompanied by a clip donning a Victorian Period-aesthetic, and it's made complete with dandyish black and white characters that look cut out from a Lewis Carroll cautionary tale. Like a Carroll anecdote, too, the video's line between fantasy and nightmare is effectively nonexistent.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?058097</url></doc>
